nl_questions: Which singles by Yuki Uchida had an Oricon rank of 2 or higher between 1995 and 1999, including their titles and release dates?

SELECT `Romaji title`, `Japanese title`, `Release date`, `Reference`, `Oricon`

nl_questions: In descending order of power, which Volvo V70 engines have more power than the average power of all engines?
sql_queries:
SELECT `Model name`, `Power (ps)` as Power, `Torque (Nm@rpm)` as Torque, `Displacement (cm³)` as Displacement, `Engine code`, `Comment`
FROM `Volvo V70`
WHERE `Power (ps)` > (SELECT AVG(`Power (ps)`) FROM `Volvo V70`)
ORDER BY `Power (ps)` DESC;

What is the total number of votes summed from Bello, Ben-Tahir, Doucet, Furtenbacher, Gauthier, Haydon, Larter, Lawrance, Libweshya, and Liscumb for each ward?
sql_queries:
SELECT `Ward`, SUM(`Bello`) + SUM(`Ben-Tahir`) + SUM(`Doucet`) + SUM(`Furtenbacher`) + SUM(`Gauthier`) + SUM(`Haydon`) + SUM(`Larter`) + SUM(`Lawrance`) + SUM(`Libweshya`) + SUM(`Liscumb`) as `Total Votes`
FROM `table_1_11447995_2`
GROUP BY `Ward`
ORDER BY `Total Votes` DESC;

nl_questions: What is the combined count of all diseases for each year?
sql_queries:
SELECT 
    `Year`, 
    SUM(`Typhus`) + SUM(`Typhoid fever`) + SUM(`Relapsing fever`) + SUM(`Smallpox`) + SUM(`Malaria`) AS `Total Disease Incidence`
FROM 
    `table_1_1007688_1`
GROUP BY 
    `Year`
ORDER BY 
    `Year` ASC;

nl_questions: What is the range of goals scored by the team across the seasons?
sql_queries:
SELECT 
    `Season`, 
    AVG(`Points`) as `Average Points`, 
    SUM(CASE WHEN `Standing` = '2nd OHA' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as `Second Place Seasons`, 
    COUNT(*) as `Total Seasons`, 
    MIN(`Goals for`) as `Lowest Goals For`, 
    MAX(`Goals for`) as `Highest Goals For`, 
    AVG(`Pct %`) as `Average Percentage`
FROM 
    `table_1_1143966_1`
GROUP BY 
    `Season`
ORDER BY 
    `Average Points` DESC;
comments: lots of irrelevant stuff, like when the teams rank was 2 OHA

    COUNT(`feminine`) AS `Count of Feminine`, 
    COUNT(`neuter`) AS `Count of Neuter`
FROM 
    table_1_10494429_3

    `case`;

nl_questions: What is the name and tenure of the most senior member listed?
sql_queries:
SELECT 
    `Representative`, 
    `Begin Date`, 
    `End Date`, 
    `Age (years, days)` 
FROM 
    `table_1_10284385_1` 
WHERE 
    `Age (years, days)` = (
        SELECT 
            MAX(`Age (years, days)`) 
        FROM 
            `table_1_10284385_1`
    );
comments: ambigious on whether most senior is refering to age or tenure
